The Telegraph - Calcutta : International
 Saturday, April 24, 2004 				 Loos to appear on dating show
				 	 Rebecca LoosLondon, April 23 (Reuters): Rebecca Loos, the woman who claims she slept with England soccer captain David Beckham, is to take part in a television dating show tomorrow.																								A spokeswoman for ITV said today the former personal assistant to Beckham would appear on prime-time programme Love On A Saturday Night as a celebrity date in a contest called Win Loos or Draw. 																								Tomorrows show is the latest in a string of media appearances for the 26-year-old Loos since she made the allegations in a tabloid newspaper nearly three weeks ago. Her publicist Max Clifford said Loos, the daughter of a Dutch diplomat, had made 800,000 through media interviews already.																								ITV said Loos would be paid for her appearance but could not confirm the venue for the date would be Madrid.
